data.description: Come and see this beautiful 2 story in the heart of The Woodlands. This house will make you feel right at home. Enter the front and be greeted by tile floors throughout the downstairs and the stairway straight ahead. The formal office with built-in shelving is on the right. Move through the dining room on the left, and you will reach The beautiful and well-maintenance kitchen with gorgeous granite countertops and dark-stained wood cabinets along with Stainless Steel Appliances. Come to the breakfast room and peek out the window at the big backyard and gazebo (a special area of this house), along with a nice-sized storage shed! All of the bedrooms are on the second floor, with the master separated on the left side of the stairway. Upstairs flooring is carpet in the master and walk-in closet as well as in bedroom 2 and laminated flooring in the hall and bedroom 3. This house has much to offer! Don't miss this opportunity! (buyer to independently verify room dimensions)
